{
  "stem": "56.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And unfortunately, that afternoon, they took her daughter anyhow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So she was left just with the other daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And whatever I got, I always felt, I-- I'd like to share it with this woman and her daughter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "She represented a mother to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was a mother with a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we saw the gypsies every morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, one day we got up, there were no more gypsies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we heard rumors that they burned the gypsies that night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're gonna be next.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he gave me-- he handed me a big container with soup and a bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started walking back with it, thinking how happy my cousin is gonna be and my friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot to tell you that I took my cousin and some friends with me on the bunk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the super bunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were only six, and it was paradise in the super bunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So on the way back, there was a [GERMAN], which means everybody's supposed to be back inside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had still some way to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a Hungarian girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody knew her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[HUNGARIAN] means red in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she had red hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was as bad as the Germans, or maybe worse, and-- even though she was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she was working for them like nobody, and with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she was coming towards me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I started to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She chased me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- I knew that if she catches me she's going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I hid in another cell block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, afterwards, I went back, and I said, I'll never again go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I-- I got so scared, I said, I won't go.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
